Ganapath trailer starring Tiger Shroff and Kriti Sanon in the lead dropped today and fans have shown quite an interest in it. Continue reading “Tiger Shroff Impresses With ‘New Avatar,’ While Kriti Sanon And Amitabh Bachchan Steal The Limelight In Ganapath’s Trailer!”

Actors Deepika Padukone and Hrithik Roshan have completed the Italy schedule of their film “Fighter.” Continue reading “It’s A Wrap For Hrithik Roshan And Deepika Padukone’s ‘Fighter’ Schedule In Italy”

Ranveer Singh has delivered some hefty performances in films like Bajirao Mastani, Padmaavat and his recent one, Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani.

Continue reading “Ranveer Singh Bumps Into MS Dhoni And Takes Selfies With The Ex-Cricket Captain”

Alia Bhatt has been receiving praise and appreciation for delivering amazing performances in successful films, which includes her most recent one, Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani.

Continue reading “Alia Bhatt Drops Behind-The-Scenes PICS As She Begins Filming For Vasan Bala’s ‘Jigra’”

Karan Johar is back with the 8th season of the popular reality show Koffee with Karan. Continue reading “Ajay Devgn And Rohit Shetty Film For Karan Johar’s Koffee With Karan 8 Before Leaving For Singham Again Shoot”

Aashiqui is one of the superhit film franchises, and that’s why there’s excitement around Aashiqui 3 as well. Continue reading “Kartik Aaryan To Romance Tara Sutaria In Anurag Basu’s Next Film?”

Pakistani actress Mahira Khan tied the knot for the second time with businessman Salim Karim in an intimate ceremony recently. Continue reading “WATCH: Mahira Khan Shares Dreamy Glimpses From Her Wedding To Salim Karim, As Sania Mirza And Sonam Kapoor React”

Shweta Bachchan is one proud mum while Jaya Bachchan is one proud grandmother, all thanks to the event that happened over the weekend. Continue reading “Shweta Bachchan And Jaya Bachchan Admits Holding Back Tears As Navya Naveli Nanda Makes Her Ramp Walk Debut At Paris Fashion Week”

Boney Kapoor opened up about Sridevi’s death for the very first time and answered questions of him being behind her ultimate demise. Continue reading “Boney Kapoor Opens Up About Going Through Lie Detector Tests After The Demise Of Sridevi, Says “She Would Have Blackouts Due To Crash Diets””
